{"tid":1427507,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭斯想制裁中國！！","createTime":"2019-08-07T06:29:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T07:03:36.000Z","uid":288601,"like":55,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bc81ef9bd95c7fabc2c56bdf2a0cec05d27f761c","tid":1427507,"uid":288601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:29:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">制裁來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\nPence signals openness to sanctions over China's human rights abuses<br />\n<br />\nVice President Mike Pence has signaled that the Trump administration is open to using the <span style=\"color: red;\">Global Magnitsky Act to sanction top officials in Xinjiang, China</span>, where more than 1 million Uighur Muslims are being held in internment camps, according to a Chinese religious freedom advocate who met with Pence at the White House Monday.<br />\n<br />\nDriving the news: Bob Fu, founder of ChinaAid, said that Pence also told him that he planned to give a second speech about China in the fall to address religious freedom issues. Beijing has been paying close attention to Pence's plans for a second speech, as the vice president has been at the forefront of the administration's confrontation with China. So hawkish was a speech Pence gave in October that the New York Times framed it as a portent of a &quot;New Cold War.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.axios.com/pence-china-uighur-xinjiang-magnitsky-sanctions-9a1aa312-7635-46bd-9576-360d36481158.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2Fpence-china-uighur-xinjiang-magnitsky-sanctions-9a1aa312-7635-46bd-9576-360d36481158.html&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75Z0XpujcHphTkFDN4g7DGnHE%3D&h=c1b471e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.axios.com/pence-china-uighur-xinjiang-magnitsky-sanctions-9a1aa312-7635-46bd-9576-360d36481158.html</a><br />\n<br />\n全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">該法案將授權於總統，可以對任何非美國公民予以制裁，包括禁止入境、凍結相關個人（或者組織）的財產</span>；但該項制裁不應涉及聯合國總部、美國與聯合國有協議的以及美國應該遵守的國際義務。其制裁的主要對象為：對非法處決、酷刑或嚴重侵犯人權事件負有責任的政府官員，以及妨礙那些為爭取或促進人權的個人或組織的官員；包括上述官員的代理人，不分官階高低，甚至包括非政府協力人員；有嚴重腐敗或受賄行為的官員；為上述人員提供便利的或轉移其非法收入的或提供其他技術支持的相關人員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E9%A6%AC%E6%A0%BC%E5%B0%BC%E8%8C%A8%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E5%95%8F%E8%B2%AC%E6%B3%95&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75Z0XpujcHphTkFDN4g7DGnHE%3D&h=64f0be76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">777睇路啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"2e707726331865f29e185e5d9fbe9f5ea7ac98f7","tid":1427507,"uid":288601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:29:30.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"fdbe5afeff4bef91075cde56d48ab51f66968f3e","tid":1427507,"uid":288601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:29:52.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"26990b49635e8cc5877914dca19409df5cf74eb3","tid":1427507,"uid":288601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:30:17.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"def8e141bef4dad9a96a3c42bbfa8f592f1064bf","tid":1427507,"uid":288601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:30:34.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"7490eee058a6b5c37a8b3983f33865a31377b38f","tid":1427507,"uid":288601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:30:57.000Z","msg":"5"